history.content:
Hi all!

Would you like to learn more about Cognitive Science and earn 1 P/NP unit? We have the Broca Decal for it! And there are still seats available!

The Broca Decal is a unique opportunity to meet with researchers in the fields of Computer Science, Neuroscience, Psychology, Linguistics and more! Class meets in Barrows 174 every Thursday from 6:00 pm to 8:00 pm.

To learn more about it and details please visit https://decal.berkeley.edu/courses/4804. Feel free to email us at broca.decal@gmail.com with any questions you may have.

Thank you!
